ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: if you are lucky enough to get a good TF, then you will have a good time with this course. If not, you will consistantly hear your fellow classmates in other groups talk about all that they have learned in discussion and feel like you might as well have taken an online course, because your course was so different from theirs.

A great learning experience and insight into the history and future of the economic, political and social situation in China. Taught by a great lecturer who has a wealth of experience and is very welcoming to student questions and interest.
Yes, if you're relatively new to Chinese issues
TA is good but it would be great if they are more responsive

comments: How could it deepen my knowlege beyond the lecture course
